Janis Hansen (manager) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Janis_Hansen_(manager) 0 Janis Ann Hansen (born June 14, 1940) is an American talent agent and retired actress.
Raised in Jamestown, and later Lakewood, both in Chautauqua County, New York, Hansen is the daughter of Roger, an accountant, and Jeanette Hansen. Her elder sister was Sheryn Rae (Mrs. Huff; born August 8, 1938 – died January 14, 2011). The sisters attended Southwestern High School in Jamestown, New York, graduating in 1955 and 1958, respectively.
